However, this work would also imply that there exist faculties which potentially allow the apprehension of structure beyond that which might be provided by 'strict' UG. SGP specifically allows structures involving parallel comparisons to occur 'automatically' on a seemingly arbitrary large scale, and if UG does not enable this, then SGP may be required to explain bias towards the apprehension of such structures, which would include poetic conventions.}
\par \pard\plain \s0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\nowidctlpar\cf0\kerning1\hich\af0\langfe2052\dbch\af0\afs24\lang1081\loch\f0\fs24\lang3081{\rtlch \ltrch\loch
